  "detailed_description": "<h1>OUR GAMES</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>NEXT</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>An arcade game. You have to use the ball to destroy figures on the level to go further.<br>Use the mouse or keyboard (WASD) to control the platform and hit the ball. If you miss the ball, then the level will begin again.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195170/extras/e291032464bb3ad333fe76ad8557a34c.poster.avif?t=1619039151\" width=512 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195170/extras/e291032464bb3ad333fe76ad8557a34c.webm?t=1619039151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195170/extras/e291032464bb3ad333fe76ad8557a34c.mp4?t=1619039151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In the game you will find 50 levels of different difficulty.<br></li><li>Beautiful atmosphere<br></li><li>Interesting bonuses that will help you<br></li><li>Traps trying to hurt you<br></li><li>Time will fly by!</li></ul><br>Earn points, multiply them with your reaction, because each level is your personal record!",
